WHAT: all
WHERE: all, -home, -prison
WHEN: 0-24
WHO: none
OTHER: PercentageVampires > 0 && !Player.isRace(Vampire)

    SceneStart()
        If isModEnabled(rk_vin_Base)
            UrgeToPeeEnable = rk_VB_UrgeToPeeEnable.getGlobal()
            UrgeToPee = Player.getActorVar(rk_VB_UrgeToPee)
            Hunger = Player.getActorVar(rk_VB_Hunger)
            HungerEnable = rk_VB_EnableHunger.getGlobal()
            "I was just going about my business as usual when suddenly a pale figure appeared from the shadows to make a dash for my neck." 
            Actor = generatePersonTemporary()
            Actor.blendPreset(Vampire)
            Actor.dress()
            Actor.show()
            Actor.moveToPersonStand(Player, 40)
            Player.animate(martialart)
            "It's a vampire! Thankfully, I managed to react in time. I'm now trying to desperately fight off my vampire attacker."
            Actor.animate(martialart)
            "As luck would have it, another pale figure appeared out of nowhere. I was freaked out for a moment, thinking it was an accomplice."
            Actor2 = generatePersonTemporary()
            While !Player.isInterestedIn(Actor2)
                Actor2 = generatePersonTemporary()
            EndWhile
            Actor2.makeInterested(Player)
            Actor2.blendPreset(Vampire)
            Actor2.dress()
            Actor2.show()
            Actor2.moveToPersonStand(Actor, 40)
            Actor2.animate(martialart)
            "To my surprise, this stranger attacked my attacker instead and helped me. Overwhelmed by <Actor2.his_or_her> strength, my attacker turned and ran away."
            Actor(Angry)::"You traitor, the High Council will be informed of your treachery!"
            Actor2(Serene):: "It's people like you who give us a bad name! We must attack the bad guys, not the good citizens..."
            Actor.animate()
            Actor2.animate()
            Actor.hide()
            "My rescuer introduces <Actor2.himself_or_herself> as <Actor2.name>. <Actor2.He_or_She> doesn't hide the fact that <Actor2.he_or_she>'s a blood-sucking vampire, but soon reassures me that <Actor2.he_or_she>'s part of a growing number of law-abiding vampires who only feed on animal blood obtained from butcher's shops."
            "While animal blood is inferior in quality, <Actor2.name> believes it's the most ethical solution to their community's dilemma of surviving while acting as a well-adjusted member of society."
            "<Actor2.name> does seem very well-adjusted and charming even. Soon enough, <Actor2.he_or_she> asks me out on a date and promises to show me a better side of vampires."
            0:: "Go on a date with <Actor2.him_or_her>"
            1:: "Exchange numbers for another time"
            2:: "Reject <Actor2.him_or_her>"
            
            If 0
                Actor2.makePermanent()
                exchangeContact(Actor2)
                endDate()
                Actor2.startDate()
            ElseIf 1
                "<Actor2.name> seems interesting, but let's not rush it."
                Actor2.makePermanent()
                exchangeContact(Actor2)
            Else
                Player(Sad):: "Thank you for your help today. But I'm already with someone."
            EndIf
        EndIf
    SceneEnd() // Improved by Raddeck
    timeout(300, vampire_legal)